name: The (Mac/Linux to Windows) Executable Builder for Python
tagline: Build Windows exes on your OS X or Linux computer
body:
# Build Windows exes on your OS X or Linux computer

This script allows you to build Windows executables using PyInstaller - without Windows!

All you need is [Wine](http://winehq.org).

Refer to the README for more information.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
